room_title: Escape room "The Uptown Murder" by The Escape Omaha in Omaha
review: What an awesome experience! I will come back until I escape every room! One down, two to go!!

room_title: Escape room "The Uptown Murder" by The Escape Omaha in Omaha
review: Had a great time! We did the Uptown Murder room and made it out in just over 43 minutes. It was definitely challenging but no so difficult as to make it frustrating. The staff was great and I would love to go back and try one of the other rooms some time!

room_title: Escape room "The Uptown Murder" by The Escape Omaha in Omaha
review: This was the first time my girl and I have ever tried anything like this and we had a blast!! Definitely can't wait to try more!!

room_title: Escape room "The Uptown Murder" by The Escape Omaha in Omaha
review: Had a great time (and not just because we got out) and the staff was fun and welcoming. Highly recommended!!!

room_title: Escape room "The Uptown Murder" by The Escape Omaha in Omaha
review: Awesome staff!! Wonderful experience! They were so helpful in helping my friends and boyfriend to set up a surprise proposal for me!! It was such a special day!! We will be back again

room_title: Escape room "The Uptown Murder" by The Escape Omaha in Omaha
review: This place is awesome!! Just hubby and I went and it was quite challenging but so fun! The staff was superb !

room_title: Escape room "The Uptown Murder" by The Escape Omaha in Omaha
review: This was great team building experience for my co-workers and I. I would recommend this to anyone who is interested in solving mysteries in a team atmosphere! I would love to solve all of the other mysteries they have to offer! Overall great experience!
